data.text: He started the argument of Hillary getting paid by corporations for her speeches.Bernie doesn’t speak for free.If his Campaign Strategist worked with Manafort in the Ukraine he’s as compromised as the colluders. There’s a reason Hillary didn’t join forces to put him on her ticket

Do you remember this tweet? Bernie is a silent agent of Trump to split the Democratic votes to ensure a Trump victory. He’s not a Democrat, we’ll never be a Socialist country. He’s been silent during the 1st 2 yrs of Trump. The sooner the lazy voters get that we’ll be better.

Russia is really running a sophisticated cyber warfare on the US. Folks are either uninformed, lazy, oblivious unwise. FB is severely compromised still nothing changes. Zuckerberg is too greedy I fix. Now it’s out of his control. He knowingly accepted $ for Russian hacking ads

Notice you don’t hear anything from Bernie. He’s gone silent. His campaign got the USball riled up about socialism. I must admit that was an awesome strategy, split the vote then disappear into the abyss. what was his price?Y was his strategist so close with Manafort in Ukraine?

The US was really duped! Even Bernie Sanders was part of the Russian plot to sabotage election & derail Clinton. Just learnt that his campaign strategist, Tag, worked with Manafort in Ukraine.I’m not giving Bernie any credit. I’m sure he was a willing player.What was he promised?
